15. e5 O-O 16. Bh3 {, again with higher prospects for White}) 12. f4 (12. h4)
12... O-O (12... Bg4 13. Be2) 13. Be2 Rac8 14. h4 {It is remarkable that the
tempting} Nb4 {is refuted by} 15. Nd5 $1) 8. Qd2 h5 {The alternatives do not
