$1 17. Nxe7 Qxe7 (17... Nxe7 $2 18. Qf6 $16) 18. Be3 (18. Qh3+ Kg8) 18... Qe6
19. Qd5 Rfe8 $11 {with balanced play in B. Koen - J. Kamanel del Corral, ICCF
email, 2020. The text move keeps an additional option for using the f-pawn as
