b5 (16... Bf8 17. Bc2 Bg7 18. Qf3) (16... Nfd7 17. Bc2) 17. cxb5 Nxd3 18. Qxd3
axb5 19. h3 $5 ({Black seems to be in good shape after both} 19. Qxb5 Qa5 20.
Qxa5 Rxa5 21. a4 Nxd5 22. Bd2 Rc5 23. Ne4 Rc2 24. Rfc1 Rb2 $11) ({and} 19. Qf3
Nd7 20. Ne4 f5 21. Nxd6 Bxd6 22. Bxd6 Nf6 23. Bg3 Qxd5) 19... h5 ({otherwise
Black may have trouble with the annoying bishop next to his king after both} 
19... b4 20. Qd4 Ra5 21. Bh6 Rxd5 22. Qxb4) ({and} 19... Qd7 20. Bh6 Bd8 21.
Rf2) 20. Bd2 $14) (14... Rb8 15. a4 $1) ({after} 14... Bf8 $6 {, as explained
