Re8 27. h3 {, calmly preparing the appearance of the own rooks to the g-file,
which spells gave danger for Black.}) 21. Qxh4 Qa5 $1 22. g4 Rae8 23. Bf4 Rxf5
$1 {A sensible measure.} 24. gxf5 Qc3 25. Bxd6 (25. Rae1 $5) 25... Re2 26. Rae1
